{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 8301897}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por Resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 335, de 5 de marzo de 1997, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a de Pesca del Ministerio de Econom&#xED;a, Fomento y Reconstrucci&#xF3;n, modif&#xED;case el numeral 2 de la Resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 111 de 1982, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, que autoriz&#xF3; a SOCIEDAD PESQUERA TEL LIMITADA, para realizar actividades pesqueras extracticas con la nave &quot;Venus&quot;, en el sentido de se&#xF1;alar que las actuales caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas de dicha nave son las siguientes:</div><br><br><div class=\"p\">Nombre&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;Venus&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  1773</div><div class=\"p\">Eslora de arqueo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 23,4&nbsp; &nbsp;  m</div><div class=\"p\">Manga&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6,9&nbsp; &nbsp;  m</div><div class=\"p\">Puntal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  3,6&nbsp; &nbsp;  m</div><div class=\"p\">Tonelaje de Registro Grueso&nbsp; &nbsp; 114,2</div><div class=\"p\">Tonelaje de Registro Neto&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  52,2</div><br><div class=\"p\">Capacidad de Bodega&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 170,7&nbsp; &nbsp; m3</div><div class=\"p\">Arte de Pesca&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cerco</div><br></div>", "i": 8301898}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so, 5 de marzo de 1997.- Juan Manuel Cruz S&#xE1;nchez, Subsecretario de Pesca.</div><br></div>", "i": 8301899}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "3", "numero": "335", "abrevi